kickstherabbit 2025-01-27 5:07 AM
There are many differences. The 2003 version (We Don't Care EP) is the most barebones, with tons of different synths and stuff The 2004 version (Climbing to New Lows) is largely the same as 2003, but longer The 2005 version (Time to Pretend EP) has the main synth hook during the bridge The 2007 version (Oracular Spectacular) changes all the synths, and changes the mixing and vocals, and replaces the hook in the bridge with a drum solo The 2008 single version is just a different mix of the 2007 one
